=E2=80=9D in the form =0Aof smallish angel investors.=0A=0A[4] This is not =
quite accurate, but captures the spirit of the rules <>.=0A=0A[5] There are=
 other important counter-arguments about disclosure and fraud: =0APublic in=
vestments are subject to a lot of transparency and disclosure rules, =0Aso =
it=E2=80=99s harder to do various sorts of fraud in public investments than=
