=E2=80=9Cphone calls on unrecorded lines=E2=80=9D are =0Amore complicated; =
depends on exactly where you sit.=0A=0A[8] Another solution is to restrict =
trading in a company=E2=80=99s bonds once you get =0Ainvolved in any restru=
cturing =E2=80=94 or to refuse to get involved in restructuring =0Anegotiat=
ions so you can keep trading. You just have one side, which is mostly =0Apu=
blic but sometimes flips to private and stops trading.=0A=0A[9] As this sug=
gests, the private side *could* share MNPI with the public =0Aside, but tha=
