list=E2=80=99 to track the firm=E2=80=99s investments =0Aand levels of know=
ledge. Compliance placed an issuer on the restricted list =0Awhen the publi=
c side learned MNPI about that issuer. Silver Point was =0Aprohibited from =
trading in securities of issuers on the restricted list. The =0Awatch list,=
